Title: MC+A Custom Keymatch Onebox C#
Description: This OneBox module mimics the Google Search Appliance's built-in KeyMatch functionality. By using this instead of the built-in KeyMatch feature, you can customize the C# Service implementation to provide alternative behavior that better suites your needs.  Based on http://code.google.com/p/custom-keymatch-onebox/ from Google.

Project Description
This OneBox module mimics the Google Search Appliance's built-in KeyMatch functionality. By using this instead of the built-in KeyMatch feature, you can customize the C# Service implementation to provide alternative behavior that better suites your needs. Based on http://code.google.com/p/custom-keymatch-onebox/ from Google.
